> Error: Interface 'Psr\SimpleCache\CacheInterface' not found

symfony/cache (v5.3.8)

```php
$cache = new Psr16Cache(new FilesystemAdapter('', 0, CACHE_DIR));
```

Solution:
`composer require psr/simple-cache`

